$(function () {
	var $table = $('.data-table');
	// set up overlay
	$table.disableBlock();
	// set up table sorting
	$table.stupidtable();
	$('thead th:first-child', $table).click();

	$table.on('beforetablesort', function (event, data) {
		$this = $(this);
		// add overlay while sorting
		$this.disableBlock('on');
		// move blanks to bottom
		$this.stupidTableBlanks(data);
	});

	$table.on('aftertablesort', function (event, data) {
		if (usingLazyLoadFallback)
			lazyLoadImages();
		$(this).disableBlock('off');
	});
});
$(function () {
	// table filtering
	var $table = $('.data-table');
	$table.filtable({ controlPanel: $('.table-filters') });
	$table.on('aftertablefilter', function (event) {
		if (usingLazyLoadFallback)
			lazyLoadImages();
	});
});

In [72]:
def pokemon(i):
    
    if(i<0):
        print("Invalid index ")
        return
    else:
    
        #The nuber of Pokemon
        pokemon_id=pokemon_url_soup.find_all(name='td',class_="cell-num cell-fixed")[i].text


        #The Name of the pokemon
        pokemon_Name=pokemon_url_soup.find_all(name='td',class_='cell-name')[i].text

        #The type of the pokemon
        pokemon_type= pokemon_url_soup.find_all(name='td',class_="cell-icon")[i].text

        #The total of the pokemon
        pokemon_total = pokemon_url_soup.find_all(name='td',class_="cell-total")[i].text

        #The HP of the pokemon
        pokemon_HP = pokemon_url_soup.find_all(name='td',class_="cell-num")[i+1].text

        #The Attack of the pokemon
        pokemon_Attack = pokemon_url_soup.find_all(name='td',class_="cell-num")[i+2].text

        #The Defense of the pokemon
        pokemon_Defense = pokemon_url_soup.find_all(name='td',class_="cell-num")[i+3].text


        #The SplAttack of the pokemon
        pokemon_SplAttack = pokemon_url_soup.find_all(name='td',class_="cell-num")[i+4].text
    
    
        #The SplDefense of the pokemon
        pokemon_SplDefense = pokemon_url_soup.find_all(name='td',class_="cell-num")[i+5].text
        
        #The url to the pokemon's page
        pokemon_url=pokemon_url_soup.find_all(name='tr')[i+1]
        pokemon_url=pokemon_url.find(name='a',class_='ent-name').get("href")
        

        
        temp_var=[]
        temp_var=np.array([[pokemon_id,pokemon_Name,pokemon_type,pokemon_total,pokemon_HP,pokemon_Attack,pokemon_Defense,pokemon_SplAttack,pokemon_SplDefense,pokemon_url]])
        
        Df_Pokemon = pd.DataFrame(temp_var,columns=['pokemon_id','pokemon_Name','pokemon_type','pokemon_total','pokemon_HP',
                                           'pokemon_Attack','pokemon_Defense','pokemon_SplAttack','pokemon_SplDefense','pokemon_url'])
    
        return Df_Pokemon

    #Getting the pokemon Url
    pokemon_loc_url = "https://pokemondb.net"+row
    
    
    #Getting the Location table from the page and transposing it
    tables_test = pd.read_html(requests.get(pokemon_loc_url, headers={'User-agent': 'Mozilla/5.0'}).text)[-2].T
    #Making the first row of the tble as columns,(Headers)
    tables_test.columns =  tables_test.iloc[0]
    tables_test =  tables_test[1:]
    
    #Checkin if XY exists in the columns
    if 'XY' in tables_test.columns:
        
        # Creating a dictionary to store the Location and the Pokemon Url 
        dict_ ={'Location_Column':tables_test['XY'],'pokemon_url':row}
        #Creating the Data frame of the dictionary
        Datafrme = pd.DataFrame(dict_)
        #Appending the Dataframe to a list
        list_.append(Datafrme)
    time.sleep(0.5)
    
#Creating the final DataFrame by concatenationg the list
Final_df=pd.concat(list_)
    
print(Final_df)

    df_temp=df_sample[df_sample[col]==True]
